{"tid":2119522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兇殘的老板","createTime":"2020-07-22T06:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T07:12:28.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6095d57f03a73a30443fd7236117ba22be550fa8","tid":2119522,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tiandichun1/status/1285725929873047553?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftiandichun1%2Fstatus%2F1285725929873047553%3Fs%3D21&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtBywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=b90f641b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftiandichun1%2Fstatus%2F1285725929873047553%3Fs%3D21&h=cb9e969b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tiandichun1/status/1285725929873047553?s=21</a><br />\n一个老板的家人为什么这样凶残？如果没有保护伞他们敢吗？<br />\n<br />\n河北保定市清苑区，王海波开车带着老板在高速上追尾导致车祸，两人都有受伤。随后，王海波为老板垫付4万医药费，对方家属并未罢休，将他3岁的女儿打進ICU，孩子的奶奶则是当场死亡。"},{"pid":"10a9aca742644f9ae21b6bacf1dd91c6bbbd11ab","tid":2119522,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"蝗殺蝗"}]}